    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid option for someone looking for a reliable driver that doesn't need to be showroom perfect. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable fading in the clear coat on the roof, along with various small dings and scuffs typical of daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows wear on the driver's seat bolster and some minor staining on the rear carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need suspension bushings and a tune-up in the near future. It is a dependable car that has been used regularly and maintained adequately.",
