    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a parts car. The engine currently runs roughly and will likely require a major overhaul or replacement to be reliable. The exterior has significant body wear, including several large dents and patches of rust, and the interior shows heavy staining and tears in the upholstery. While it does start, it is not recommended for long-distance driving in its current state.",
